.X Management and upkeep (Booker)
.HL 1 Management
.P
Apart from edits to the code itself, which would arise for reasons which 
I cannot forsee, the only things that I can think of that may need 
editing are :
.S
.LS
.LE;Periods - the number or times of bookings periods may in the future 
need to be edited.  This is achieved by editing the module BookLibrary.
More detail is available in the chapter on BookLibrary, but rest assured 
that BOOKER can cope fully with any changes that may be made.
.LE;Keyboards - again, the number of keyboards or the actual keyboard 
numbers may need to be changed.  See the chapter on BookLibrary.
.LE;Maximum number of bookings - again, see BookLibrary for details.
.ELS
.P
No other edits should be neccessary.  Most of the management as opposed to 
editing will be done from MASTER.
.P
